---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/ui/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Hashbooks" 
  description="Hashbooks' privacy policies and guidelines regarding how we collect, store, and secure your financial bookkeeping information."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-width-800">
      <SectionHeading 
        title="Privacy Policy"
        subtitle="Last updated: July 2026"
        align="left"
      />

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We collect information that you provide directly to us when requesting a proposal, contact inquiries, or during onboarding. This includes names, emails, phone numbers, business name, estimated transaction volumes, and financial integration keys.
        </p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use collected information solely to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide, operate, and maintain our bookkeeping services.</li>
          <li>Analyze business transaction volumes for custom proposals.</li>
          <li>Reconcile accounts and generate financial reports.</li>
          <li>Respond to contact requests and customer support inquiries.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement bank-level 256-bit encryption protocols to protect your financial and business data. Read-only integrations are configured with accounting systems where applicable, and we do not store primary credentials.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Disclosures</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personally identifiable or financial information to outside parties. This does not include trusted third parties who assist us in operating our website or conducting our services, so long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .max-width-800 {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }

  .legal-content p {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-size: var(--fs-body-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
</style>
